NAME
    libconfig - Save and load config files easily
DESCRIPTION
    The LIBCONFIG library makes saving and loading INI config files easier, as it does some things for you.
LIBRARY
    libconfig.load(filename, defaults={}, saveFile=True)
        Loads a config file and returns a configparser.ConfigParser object.
        The defaults dictionary is in the format {<section>: {<option>: <value>}, {<option>: <value>}}, where all three are strings. 
        See the source code for PKM for a good demo.
    libconfig.save(config, filename)
        Saves a configparser.ConfigParser object.
SEE ALSO
    lib: library list
    import: how to import libraries
